"Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee President: firmly believes that China has the ability to host a successful Winter Olympics during special times - Xinhua News Agency."
"Xinhua News Agency, Sarajevo, December 11th: The President of the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee, Kvešćić, recently stated that Bosnia is highly looking forward to the Beijing Winter Olympics and firmly believes that China has the ability to host a successful Winter Olympics during special times."
"Recently, the Chinese Ambassador to Bosnia and Herzegovina, Ji Ping, met with the President of the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee, Kvešćić, at the Sarajevo Olympic Center."
"During the meeting, Kvešćić actively evaluated the bilateral relationship between Bosnia and China and stated that he visited China during the Beijing Summer Olympics in 2008 and was deeply impressed by China's excellent organizational work. He firmly believes that China has the ability to host a successful Winter Olympics during special times; Bosnia is highly looking forward to the Beijing Winter Olympics and the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee is actively organizing its participation. Bosnia hopes to use this as an opportunity to carry out more extensive exchanges and cooperation with China in the field of sports."
"Ji Ping stated that China and Bosnia have a special 'Olympic link.'"
"The 1984 Sarajevo Winter Olympics were successfully held here, and in two months, the 2022 Beijing Winter Olympics will also begin, presenting a simple, safe, and exciting event to the world."
"Looking forward to deepening exchanges and cooperation in areas such as preparation for winter sports events and athlete training between the two countries, the Chinese Embassy in Bosnia is willing to continue playing a bridging role and use the Beijing Winter Olympics as an opportunity to further deepen cultural exchanges between the two countries, allowing the people of both countries to "move forward together," and wishing Bosnian athletes good results in Beijing."
Before the meeting, the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee held the "10th Annual Best Athlete" award ceremony, with Ambassador Ji Ping as the special guest, presenting the award for the best young athlete in Bosnia and Herzegovina.
The promotional video for the Beijing Winter Olympics was being played continuously at the event site.